snippet.title: Red Bull League of Its Own
snippet.description:
Europe’s finest teams are headed to Munich to test T1’s League of Legends expertise once again.
Red Bull League of Its Own makes its grand return to Germany on November 29th, taking over the SAP Garden in Munich for the third edition of the one-day invitational tournament. The pressure is on this year, as reigning champions T1 return to the stage along with some of Europe’s most celebrated teams, all going head-to-head in an unmissable end-of-year showdown set to feature exclusive match-ups and unparalleled gameplay.
